{
  "stem": "3382.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] You know, so I thank him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Don't.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And then the next day, I was transferred to a different commander.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "No, the next day I was took to a place where I could rest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It was are some kind of a-- I don't know what they did with old clothes, or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And then I was sent to a different commander.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Still, it was very bad because I was in a very bad block.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "One day, the Blockfuhrer, block leader, told me to clean the-- to work the floor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I was sitting as such, you know, and rubbing, whatever or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Through the block came in two-- as we call them, [NON-ENGLISH], you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "That was 'permanent people.' They talk something to that-- to the block.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Then one came up to me, picked me up, you know, with one hand, stood me up and said, get out from here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "This is the block not for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And they put me-- and the two put me on the block number five, one of the best in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "On one side was a group of Poles with the number 17,000 something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "It was a group of young people who [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] were denounced in Gdynia and arrested.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "On the other side were Danes and Norwegians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the time, I was, you know, with red triangle, with letter P, Pole.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there, one young Pole by the name Felix Lada started to take care of me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Little by little, he organized for me different clothes, different everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got befriended with a Dane who worked in Scheinderei.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It means in 'tailor shop.' He made for me at that shop.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
